    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>Heavy crossbows are large apparatuses designed to propel @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.snljncwjL9fnIk1o]{bolts} with great speed. They come with a quiver. They are not difficult to fire, but their weight and size make them difficult to deploy for those untrained in their use.</em></p><p>A magic ranged weapon like this one has a bonus to attack and damage rolls, <span style=\"font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif\">but doesn't necessarily deal magical damage. You need @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-magic-items.Item.3T70svzLcpNjJZAP]{Magic Bolts} to deal magical bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing damage.</span></p><p>Properties:</p><p>&amp;Reference[Magicw], &amp;Reference[Ammunition], &amp;Reference[Heavy], &amp;Reference[Loading], &amp;Reference[Handed]</p>",
